## Duty Cycling

### Sensor Duty Cycle

```
    Active         Sleep              Active         Sleep
  |------|----------------------------|------|---------------------------...
   Tsample         Tsleep              Tsample         Tsleep

  Duty cycle = Tsample / (Tsample + Tsleep)
  Average current = (Iactive * Tsample + Isleep * Tsleep) / (Tsample + Tsleep)
```

### Duty Cycle Budgeting

| Subsystem | Active Time | Sleep Time | Duty Cycle | Avg Current |
|-----------|-------------|------------|------------|-------------|
| Sensor sampling | | | | |
| Radio TX/RX | | | | |
| Processing | | | | |
| Display | | | | |
| **Total system** | | | | |

### Communication Duty Cycle

- [ ] Radio uses shortest possible TX window
- [ ] Batching: aggregate multiple readings before transmitting
- [ ] Adaptive interval: increase sleep time when data is static
- [ ] Acknowledgment timeout is bounded (prevent indefinite radio-on)

