## Battery Life Estimation

### Calculation Template

```
Battery capacity: C mAh
Average current:  I_avg mA

Battery life (hours) = C / I_avg
Battery life (days)  = C / (I_avg * 24)
```

### Margin Rules

| Factor | Value | Rationale |
|--------|-------|-----------|
| Battery self-discharge | 5-10% per year | Chemistry-dependent |
| Temperature derating | 20-40% at 0 C | Capacity drops in cold |
| Component aging | 10% over product life | Leakage increases |
| Safety margin | 20% | Unpredicted wake events |

